data.description: This duplex is in a prime area, Close to shopping centers, highways, and the new casino. It is a low maintenance, great income earning property in Cathedral City. Units are in 2 separate structures giving you room to add on to property. Owner is a licensed CA real Estate Broker. Information on property is deemed reliable but not Guaranteed. Buyer's agent to verify all information. Property is tenant occupied please do not disturb tenants they are unaware of the sale. Submit all offers subject to interior inspection.
